headline.print_headline: NASA Downplays Russian's Talk on Space Cooperation
headline.main: NASA Downplays Russian's Talk on Space Cooperation

lead_paragraph: NASA is downplaying a Russian official's statements about an earlier end to cooperation on the International Space Station because of U.S. sanctions on Moscow.
